         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Your collaborator Willkomm, 'the curls probably also shine so silver-white, whitened by the fullness of the years': I remember very well in the 40s of the century, how he discovered the  ¶ Biarum ¶ . ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">93.09.05</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Johan Lange</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Lange papers, Botanisk Centralbibliotek, Copenhagen.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">5/9/93</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>You asked me, dear Prof. Lange, in your last kind letter, to send you an other impression of a portrait of mine; but I do not remember, whether you allude to a photogram or a lithogram. Kindly let me know which, and I will gladly fulfil your wish. It is with much sorrow, that I hear of your impaired eyesight; but you have worked so long and so zealously with the microscope, that such sufferings, — distressing though they are —, come not as a surprise. My visual power is not so good now either than 1840, when I commenced to use magnifying lenses extensively.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It was very pleasing to me, that the <name key="Todea">Todea</name> arrived safely, it was the "last of the Mohikans"<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to J. Lange, 17 April 1893. M refers to J. F. Cooper, <seg style="font-style: italic; ">The last of the Mohicans</seg> (1826). M had previously told Lange that no more specimens of giant <name key="Todea">Todea</name>s were available; see M to J, Lange, 24 January 1893 (in this edition as 93-01-24a). </p>
               </note> as far as known.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Always with regardful remembrance your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Ihrem Collaboratär Willkomm "glänzen auch wohl die Locken so silberweiss gebleicht von der Fülle der Jahre":<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Slight misquotation of </seg>
                  </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.5516in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
                     xml:lang="en">Ihm glänzte die Locke silberweiß,</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.5516in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">Gebleicht von der Fülle der Jahre.</seg>
                  </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>that is, lines 33 and 34 of Schiller, ‘Der Graf von Habsburg’ (</seg>
                     <ref target="https://www.friedrich-schiller-archiv.de/gedichte-schillers/balladen-schiller/der-graf-von-habsburg/"
                          rend="Internet%20link"
                          style="color: #0563c1; ">
                        <seg rend="Internet%20link" style="color: #0563c1; ">
                           <seg style="color: #0070c0; ">https://www.friedrich-schiller-archiv.de/gedichte-schillers/balladen-schiller/der-graf-von-habsburg/</seg>
                        </seg>
                     </ref>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>accessed 24 July 2018). </seg>
                  </p>
               </note> Ich erinnere sehr wohl in den 40 Jahren des Jahrhunderts wie er das <name key="Biarum">Biarum</name> entdeckte. Grüssen Sie ihn recht freundlichst, wenn Sie ihm schreiben. Auch sein Bild hängt in meiner Studirstube (lithographisches Portrait)</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Your collaborator Willkomm, 'the curls probably also shine so silver-white, whitened by the fullness of the years': I remember very well in the 40s of the century, how he discovered the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Biarum">Biarum</name>
               </seg>.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>Willkomm (1847) described a species from Malaga, found during the two years that he spent in the Iberian peninsula; see Devesa Alcaraz &amp; Maria del Carmen (2001), pp. 274, 308.</p>
               </note> Most friendly greetings to him if you write to him. His picture also hangs in my study (lithographic portrait)</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Biarum">Biarum</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Todea">Todea</name>
            </p>
         </div>
